headline.main: Greek Economy Slumps in Fourth Quarter, Hurt by Net Exports
headline.print_headline: Greek Economy Slumps in Fourth Quarter, Hurt by Net Exports

lead_paragraph: Number eight Billy Vunipola has returned to Eddie Jones's England squad for Saturday's Six Nations clash against Scotland after recovering from a knee injury.
